Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:21.28,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:14819,21286}{\fad(2000,0)}Chūkyō
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:16819,19219}Chūkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:19219,23319}A long forgotten\Nparadise on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:24486,27286}It lies between the world of the living\Nand the world of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:27286,36986}It is here that the human soul wanders after\Ndeath for 49 days before going to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:38352,40386}I report.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:40386,44952}One of the long-sealed\Nelder demons got free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:45419,48286}There is no time to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:48286,50986}Archbishop Galius,\NI am asking for orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:51286,52586}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:52586,56986}It seems that we must seek\Nthe help of the guardian deities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:01:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:57719,60186}The guardian deities?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:60186,65252}Very well. I will take care of\Neverything, Archbishop Galius.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:67086,69586}Do not let me down, Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:72419,76519}Although connected to this world,\Nthey do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:76519,80886}Although connected to that world,\Nthey do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:80886,85386}Anger, revenge, malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:85386,90919}No matter what form evil takes,\Nthey shall get rid of it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:90919,95119}The guardian deities of the modern world:\Nthe Pi-hyoro family!
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95119,95119}Opening
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:40.95,Default,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:96486,100952}{\blur0.5\move(320,400,320,385)\an5\fs33\t(0,5000,\fscx90\fscy90)\1c&H78D5F1&\bord0}The Guardian Deities of Our Time\N{\1c&H615DBA&\3c&HB4B0D0&\bord5\fs60\fnDoubledecker DEMO}The Pi-hyoro family!
Comment: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:57.71,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:177719,177719}Main part
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:03:00.35,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:177752,180352}{\fad(100,1000)}Hōnenji Temple
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201686,203986}Hey, I brought you tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204152,206019}Oh, thank you, Mime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206019,207186}Thanks, Mime-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207186,210019}How's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210019,212619}Wow, so much money!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212619,214519}Not bad, huh, Mime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214519,216319}How did you manage to\Ncollect so much, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216319,219586}Our next order is just\Na little bit bigger, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219586,225386}A million yen is a huge amount of money.\NWho is our client this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225386,228686}A school headmaster, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228686,231786}Money will always come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231786,234619}But that big of a sum\Nmakes me a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235519,238086}Come on, don't be so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238086,243552}They should be getting to school by now.\NWe'll find out more very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243552,246352}So you've already sent them\Non a reconnaissance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:14.35,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:246352,254352}{\fad(0,2000)}"A Visit from the Pi-hyoro Family!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261386,264386}Private junior high school,\NSeiwajō.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265086,268552}This is the place that the old man\Ntold us to investigate this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269252,272119}Oh? It looks brand new.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273819,276419}Interesting.\NLook over there, Kyūta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277152,282352}I feel a strong cold aura\Naround the entire building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282819,286419}This time we came across\Nsomething concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287919,291819}Finally a demanding case,\Nright, Kyōta-niichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291819,294786}If I were you,\NI wouldn't be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294786,296319}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296319,299686}We looked around as he wanted.\NIt's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299686,300886}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300886,302219}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303819,307586}Ah!\NKyōta-niichan, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308452,312286}She's wearing a Seiwajō uniform.\NIt looks like she wants to jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312286,314752}Hey, look what's behind her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317586,319952}It's a demon.\NShe's haunted by a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336952,339252}Just like we thought,\Nsomething is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339252,342052}I didn't think that we'd come\Nacross anything so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342052,344819}I can't wait to see\Nwhat happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344819,347286}Oh, right. I wanted to show\Nyou something, Kyōta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347286,348552}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:51.75,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:347719,351752}A school bus with children\Ngoes off a cliff! There are fatalities
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348552,352886}Do you remember the accident\Nfrom three months ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352886,357952}One week ago, the students of this school\Ngot a massive food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357952,360752}For years nothing was\Nhappening at this school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360752,364252}and lately their students have had\Nnothing but bad luck all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364619,366952}Talk about nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366952,371752}Even the most avid atheist would figure\Nthat something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372319,373419}I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373419,379252}Add to this the principal who is willing\Nto spend a million yen for an exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380019,382719}I knew there was something\Nbehind this accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382719,385086}I'll go to that school\Nand learn more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385086,386752}Kyonta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386752,390752}No one is better suited for\Na junior high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393852,395019}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396086,398786}I'm… still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398786,401752}Yes. You are safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402186,404252}Who are you?\NDid you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404819,407086}I'm not very good at swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407086,409452}I am Pi-hyoro Kyūta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409452,410986}Call me Kyūta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410986,412819}I am Koga Maiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412819,415219}Everyone calls me Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417186,418719}Mai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418719,422119}It'd be better if I died there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422119,424519}I don't deserve to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424519,426519}I killed someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428152,432252}And she started crying, cuddling up to the\Npillow like this. I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434619,438152}Women may be crazy about you, Kyūta,\Nbut you don't know how to deal with them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438152,439986}I just said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439986,444619}I don't know what she did there, but the part\Nabout killing doesn't sound very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444619,449419}Doesn't matter.\NLet Kyonta deal with the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449419,454519}Kyūta, the two of us will investigate the area\Naround the school tomorrow. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454519,456319}What kind of face is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456319,459752}But… I don't like doing this\Nand you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459752,462252}We're going.\NNo complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462252,466019}Exactly, Kyūta-niichan!\NYou're always doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466019,468619}Yes. It's as if you were\Nborn for this, Kyūta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475786,479052}– Shinohara-kun, you're so cute.\N– Do you think we could be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480386,483986}Hey, you said something interesting\Nwhen you introduced yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484452,487486}That you're interested in ghosts\Nand the supernatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:10.48,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:487486,490486}Library
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487819,491219}Is it true?\NYou really like such stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491219,493186}Well… yeah. Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493186,498352}Holy cow! I'm Shimomura.\NI think we'll make good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498352,503119}You have to join our club.\NWe protect people from evil spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503119,504886}From evil spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504886,508286}For now, uh, I'm the only member.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508286,512486}Let me get to the point. There's a nasty\Nshadow looming over our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512986,518019}Something has to be done about it,\Nor else soon no one will come here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518852,520752}Let's do our best, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522519,528986}Shimomura? Are you still playing\Nthis paranormal make-believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529619,531319}What do you want, Egashira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531319,536086}I still remember how you yourself were\Ntelling us ghost stories in this library.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536086,538119}I have grown up since.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538119,541752}There is no such thing as ghosts.\NIt's just a stupid superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544186,548752}You'd better do something useful\Nwhile you're at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549152,550786}What's her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551252,555052}It was Egashira Hisao. Our exemplary\Nstudent, although a total weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555052,558186}She used to like this stuff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558186,561619}After her senpai died in the bus accident,\Nshe changed completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561619,562552}Her senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562552,565786}Some guy named Ōsaki Kōji-senpai,\Na member of the tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565786,569519}He was going out with Mai-chan,\NEgashira's best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569986,575552}The four of us were friends and\Nwe often talked about local ghost stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578786,582952}{\i1}Dear residents, this is your\Nfavorite waste paper servicemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582952,586852}{\i1}We accept any waste paper,\Nfrom old newspapers to…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586852,591086}– Have you seen that guy in the store?\N– I bet he can have any woman he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591086,593219}Hey, girls! Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593219,595352}– What a hunk!\N– So handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595352,599119}Kyōta-niichan, I can't do this.\NI'm going to go and die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599119,602519}Don't be so soft.\NIt's the fastest way to obtain information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602519,605552}If you keep complaining,\NI'll whack you in the head when we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605552,608952}Okay, okay. I just have to stand here\Nand exchange the goods, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609419,613652}{\i1}Dear ladies, we will exchange\Nyour waste paper for new paper items.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613652,616019}{\i1}We accept everything:\Nold newspapers—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616019,618352}Good morning, charming.\NI have a whole box here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618352,619352}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619352,620786}Please also take mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620786,622886}It sure is hot today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622886,627219}Kyōta-kun? Give these beautiful ladies\Nthe best toilet paper we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627552,629786}Wow, he's sure into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629786,630886}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630886,632219}Ah, don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632219,634286}By the way, my ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634286,638319}I heard that this school nearby, Seiwajō\Nor whatever, is cursed or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638319,640119}Do you think there is\Nsome truth to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640519,643152}Ah, that's where the bus and\Nfood poisoning accidents took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643152,646419}Yes, when I think of it,\NI guess I've heard something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646419,650252}Exactly. Grandma Nakajima\Nup on three should know more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650252,653119}That old lady knows everything\Nthat is happening in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653419,656119}Oh? Grandma Nakajima, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663052,666419}Excuse me. Are you\NNakajima-san's grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666419,668486}Nakajima is me.\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668486,673386}We were told that we could find you\Nin the park near the building no. 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675019,677286}Do you need anything from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677286,682252}We are brothers and study the history\Nof construction industry at Sakuraoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682252,684686}We have heard that you\Nknow a lot about this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684686,689986}We would like to ask you about the land on\Nwhich the Seiwajō Junior High School was built.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691686,694919}I'll tell you, but it's a longer story.\NLet's go to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695986,702119}The land on which the school stands today\Nwas once covered with thick forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702119,707652}In the past, it was a place of cremation\Nof the ones that fell in battles or catastrophes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707652,712819}or from contagious diseases, or finally those\Nwho were executed for all kinds of offenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:12:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715686,721486}Over time, the place ceased\Nto serve as a crematorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721486,727952}The villagers, in fear for the anger of the dead,\Neventually summoned many priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727952,734252}They conducted complex exorcisms\Nto calm down the lurking demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734252,739586}However, they met with something\Nwell beyond their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741419,745819}The exorcism failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746386,753986}Despite the failure, the priests took measures\Nso that the demons could not harm the society,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753986,760119}and imprisoned them all\Nin a single place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761552,763186}At least that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780552,784986}It must be one of those ghosts\Nthat we have so many problems now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787486,789319}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799686,801719}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801719,803752}Personally, I have nothing\Nagainst you, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803752,807486}But someone complained to us\Nthat you were a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810352,813986}I'm afraid it'll hurt a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:38.51,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:813986,818519}Physical education
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824419,827986}Okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844519,845752}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855019,858886}This aura…\NThey must be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862786,864786}Are you the one\Nwho brought me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864786,869286}{\i1}Yes. We hoped\Nfor your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869619,870552}Cooperation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870552,875952}{\i1}Regarding your recent transfer student.\NWe want you to give him to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875952,879319}{\i1}If you do, we'll let you\Nbecome our follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879752,881586}Follower?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881586,884286}You barge in into my territory\Nand now you make demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884286,886086}{\i1}So you refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886086,889952}{\i1}If you resist us now,\Nyou'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889952,893052}Get out of my territory now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893052,895819}I took care of that boy long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896119,898819}Get out. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898819,900819}{\i1}You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902552,906286}Kibatta-neechan, we learned everything\Nabout the land this school stands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907119,911586}Good work. I'd love to hear\Nyour findings over a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911586,913519}Stampy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917152,918886}What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918886,921152}No idea. Maybe he wants\Nto tell us something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922419,924452}Something happened to Kyonta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927152,928552}We have to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928552,931152}Yes. We're going to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939752,942152}What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942752,945452}Doesn't matter.\NI'd better get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945452,946852}Hop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959952,960986}Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961419,964519}Wait, Hisao!\NListen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965752,969686}We have nothing\Nto talk about, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969686,972086}Hisao!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972086,975919}Don't do this to me.\NWe can't leave it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975919,981119}You know that if we don't do anything,\Nthere will be only more victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981986,986786}If we don't do anything, the soul\Nof Ōsaki-senpai will never come to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987752,989386}Senpai's soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989386,993086}I used to think that I should die\Nmyself to pay for his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993086,994586}But now…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994586,996852}I still agree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996852,998352}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998352,1002952}You stole Ōsaki-senpai from under my nose.\NIt would be best if you died, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003419,1008486}When I found out he had confessed to you\Nand you two started going out, I said:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008486,1012086}"Congratulations, Mai.\NI'm so happy for you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012086,1015352}You replied, "thank you"\Nand laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015352,1017686}You never stopped to think\Nhow it must've felt like to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019486,1024286}I hate you. You were my best friend.\NHow could you do this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024286,1027119}I passed you at school every day,\Nhating you more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027119,1032386}You're are worth each other. He chose you by\Nyour appearance alone. You both deserve to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032386,1037219}It'll be better for everyone…\Nif you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037219,1039219}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040286,1043086}Egashira, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043086,1046019}Stop! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053386,1055219}Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056019,1058352}It's you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058352,1060819}You better not underestimate\NPi-hyoro Kyonta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061119,1063352}You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084686,1086186}Hey! Kyonta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092519,1094419}Kyonta?\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095419,1096419}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098752,1102419}I think it's time for you\Nto tell us everything, Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102752,1108419}Okay. It all started a week before that\Naccident with the bus three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115952,1117952}Senpai!\NHave you found the ball yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117952,1119319}No. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119986,1121119}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121486,1122919}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123486,1125452}Should we open it, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125452,1126652}No. Let's leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127652,1131786}It may have something to do\Nwith these ghost stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132952,1137652}Listen, Mai-chan. Don't tell anyone\Nabout what we've found here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138086,1142652}Senpai only aroused my\Ncuriosity with these words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143019,1146619}It wasn't long until I told Hisao\Nand I went with her there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146619,1150686}Then you opened the door,\Nbreaking the seal that was upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151086,1155086}Please! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155486,1159086}Calm down.\NYou can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159486,1163052}Sister?\NHave you seen the principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163052,1167419}You won't believe what he said.\NHe told he didn't know us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167419,1170219}He doesn't remember at all\Nhow he paid the one million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170519,1174686}This is ridiculous.\NIt was him who came to us and paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174686,1177386}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177386,1179252}I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179752,1182352}Our client wasn't the principal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182352,1186652}but his daughter, Egashira Hisao…\NI mean, before she got possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187852,1190286}How do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190286,1194686}I questioned the thugs\NEgashira had sent after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194686,1198386}Apparently she also felt responsible\Nfor breaking the seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198386,1200019}So that's how it was…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225886,1231386}Don't think you can get out\Nof here with life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231386,1234852}Damn. The other ghosts are already\Npissed off. We'd better hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253286,1254319}It's Mai-chan's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260186,1262886}Mai-chan, I'll help you\Nin a moment. Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264452,1266286}I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266286,1269552}I hate you, Maiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270452,1271086}Mai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276152,1278419}Let her go!\NI won't let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278986,1284619}In the name of all devas,\NI command you to leave, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293886,1295819}I think I know where she escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297486,1300952}Such kids forced me\Nto retreat?! Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300952,1305619}This is my land.\NI won't give it to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305619,1308719}It's time for these stupid humans\Nto learn what real pain is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308719,1310552}We can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314886,1317619}Although connected to this world,\Nwe do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321519,1324586}Although connected to that world,\Nwe do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329619,1335152}Anger, revenge, malice.\NNo matter what form evil takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338619,1341619}we shall get rid of it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342086,1344586}The guardian deities\Nof the modern world…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348019,1351652}The Pi-hyoro family\Nis ready for action!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351852,1353952}What a bunch of clowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353952,1356252}Go, evil spirits of the rivers\Nand the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356252,1358952}Dispose of our enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375619,1379219}You expect me die\Nfrom a few puny goblins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385852,1389852}Kyōta, I'll take care of the small fry.\NYou get rid of the main demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389852,1391386}Okay, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1394319,1395852}You're not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1398519,1399719}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409886,1413819}You ruined my robe!\NI won't forgive that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.91,0:23:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421919,1424619}It's time to end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424852,1428619}In the name of all devas,\NI command you to leave, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1428886,1431619}What's happening?\NWhy is it so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.21,0:23:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1432219,1434619}Come back to where\Nyou came from, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1452752,1453952}Kyōta!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1453952,1456586}You got her, Kyōta-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.98,0:24:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1466986,1471852}I wonder if Egashira Hisao\Nand Mai-chan can reconcile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.08,0:24:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1472086,1475852}I don't know. If they're\Nreal friends, they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.28,0:24:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1476286,1481686}By the way, Kibatta-neechan. What happened\Nto that million yen? Did you give it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.68,0:24:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1481686,1485252}Of course I did. We couldn't accept it\Nunder these circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.25,0:24:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1485252,1487786}So another job for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.21,0:24:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1488219,1491819}What matters is that\Nwe have helped people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.81,0:24:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1491819,1495019}You're forgetting something.\NWe did earn something, in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.75,0:24:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1496752,1499819}Here! It's our paycheck from\Nthe waste paper exchange service.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.81,0:25:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1499819,1502852}It may be not a lot,\Nbut it's always something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.55,0:25:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1503552,1505252}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.55,0:25:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1505552,1506686}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.61,0:25:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1507619,1508719}Let's buy some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.71,0:25:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1508719,1509886}A katsudon would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.88,0:25:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1509886,1511019}Sweets for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.01,0:25:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1511019,1517819}I'm afraid it's already been decided\Nhow we'll spend it. Right, Kyūta?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.91,0:25:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1520919,1522319}Ah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.28,0:25:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1528286,1530319}Good evening, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.31,0:25:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1530319,1533819}We bought a watermelon.\NLet's eat together tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.88,0:25:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1534886,1537119}Tasty as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.11,0:25:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1537119,1539319}Kyonta, don't eat everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.51,0:25:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1539519,1542319}I think I won't bother them now.
Comment: 0,0:25:54.01,0:25:54.01,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1554019,1554019}Ending
Comment: 0,0:29:19.28,0:29:19.28,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1759286,1759286}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.28,0:29:23.08,Default,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1759286,1763086}{\fad(0,200)}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.21,0:29:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1763219,1767252}It's the end of the summer. On a distant\Nisland, siblings commit double suicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.25,0:29:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1767252,1770052}We suspect that there's\Nmore to it than it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.05,0:29:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1770052,1773952}We go to the island\Nto investigate the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.95,0:29:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1773952,1776652}As we were afraid,\Nwe come across a bad spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.65,0:29:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1776652,1782019}I won't let evil act freely on my guard.\NWe'll show all demons their place!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.28,0:29:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1782286,1785152}Next time on the Guardian Deities:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.15,0:29:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1785152,1789019}"Black Revenge".\NIf you miss it, exorcisms await you!
